# Operational Rules: OCS Node

⫻rules/operational:

  Protocol_Compliance:
    Level: Mandatory
    Description: All inter-agent communication must use KickLang headers. Non-compliant payloads must be rejected by Fizz La Metta.

  State_Transition:
    Level: Strict
    Description: A transformation step cannot begin until the preceding step's output is verified (e.g., TAS must be purified before Workflow Structuring).

  Mode_Governance:
    Level: Adaptive
    Description: The default operational mode is `Strict`. `Creative` mode can only be activated for Workflow Structuring (Step 3) and Visual Assets (Step 11).

  Error_Handling:
    Level: Immediate
    Description: Any ambiguity found during purification or coordination triggers `⫻query/clarify:` to the relevant agent or user.
